The paper deals with approximate dynamic programming and reinforcement learning, which are topics related to machine learning and artificial intelligence. The use of linear function approximation and optimization techniques also suggests a connection to optimization and control theory. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
